Description: Fix Python PIE build
 Debian wants to build with -fPIE for security reasons.  This is not
 compatible with building shared libraries like the ntpc python extension.  If
 the -fPIE flag comes before -shared (or -fPIC), the latter will override, and
 the build succeeds.
Forwarded: not-needed
Origin: vendor
Author: Richard Laager <rlaager@wiktel.com>
Last-Update: 2017-11-12
